      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "HandleCookingStation(station)\n\nIF station.IsIdle:\n  -> RecipeSelectUI.Instance.Open(station)\n  -> Player selects recipe\n  -> RequestStartCooking(station, idx)\n  -> StartCookingRpc(netId, recipeIndex)\n\nIF station.IsDone:\n  -> CollectDishRpc(netId)\n\nIF station.IsBurned:\n  -> ClearStationRpc(netId)", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "HandleCookingStation(station)\n\nIF station.IsIdle:\n  -> RecipeSelectUI.Instance.Open(station)\n  -> Player selects recipe\n  -> RequestStartCooking(station, idx)\n  -> StartCookingRpc(netId, recipeIndex)\n\nIF station.IsDone:\n  -> CollectDishRpc(netId)\n\nIF station.IsBurned:\n  -> ClearStationRpc(netId)", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },


