      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Resolve stationNetId -> NetworkObject\n2. GetComponent<CookingStation>()\n3. ValidateTeam(OwnerClientId, station.TeamId)\n4. ValidateProximity(station.transform.position)\n5. station.ClearStation()\n   -> Resets to Idle, progress = 0", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Resolve stationNetId -> NetworkObject\n2. GetComponent<CookingStation>()\n3. ValidateTeam(OwnerClientId, station.TeamId)\n4. ValidateProximity(station.transform.position)\n5. station.ClearStation()\n   -> Resets to Idle, progress = 0", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },


