      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "1. Resolve counterNetId -> NetworkObject\n2. GetComponent<ServingCounter>()\n3. ValidateTeam(OwnerClientId, counter.TeamId)\n4. ValidateProximity(counter.transform.position)\n5. counter.AddDish(recipeIndex)\n   -> platedDishes.Count < maxDishes (3)?\n   -> NetworkList<int>.Add(recipeIndex)\n6. CarriedItem.Value = Empty", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Resolve counterNetId -> NetworkObject\n2. GetComponent<ServingCounter>()\n3. ValidateTeam(OwnerClientId, counter.TeamId)\n4. ValidateProximity(counter.transform.position)\n5. counter.AddDish(recipeIndex)\n   -> platedDishes.Count < maxDishes (3)?\n   -> NetworkList<int>.Add(recipeIndex)\n6. CarriedItem.Value = Empty", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },


