      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "After server validates & executes:\n\nCarriedItem.Value changes\n  -> OnValueChanged fires on ALL clients\n  -> WritePermission: Server only\n\nCookingStation.StationState changes\n  -> CookProgress synced at ~10Hz (0.1s)\n  -> Status: Idle/Cooking/Done/Burned\n\nServingCounter.platedDishes (NetworkList)\n  -> OnListChanged fires on ALL clients", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "After server validates & executes:\n\nCarriedItem.Value changes\n  -> OnValueChanged fires on ALL clients\n  -> WritePermission: Server only\n\nCookingStation.StationState changes\n  -> CookProgress synced at ~10Hz (0.1s)\n  -> Status: Idle/Cooking/Done/Burned\n\nServingCounter.platedDishes (NetworkList)\n  -> OnListChanged fires on ALL clients", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

