      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "CookingStation Lifecycle (Server)", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "CookingStation Lifecycle (Server)", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "type": "text", "version": 2, "versionNonce": 822, "isDeleted": false, "id": "cl_body",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "x": 1140, "y": 582, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 330, "height": 80, "seed": 822, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "text": "Idle -> StartCooking() -> Cooking\n  TickCooking(): progress += dt/cookTime\n  Sync at ~10Hz via SYNC_INTERVAL (0.1s)\n\nCooking -> progress >= 1.0 -> Done\n  burnTimer = settings.burnTimeAfterDone\n  GameEvents.CookingCompleted()\n\nDone -> burnTimer <= 0 -> Burned\n  TickBurnTimer() counts down", "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Idle -> StartCooking() -> Cooking\n  TickCooking(): progress += dt/cookTime\n  Sync at ~10Hz via SYNC_INTERVAL (0.1s)\n\nCooking -> progress >= 1.0 -> Done\n  burnTimer = settings.burnTimeAfterDone\n  GameEvents.CookingCompleted()\n\nDone -> burnTimer <= 0 -> Burned\n  TickBurnTimer() counts down", "lineHeight": 1.25
    },


